        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"jbolger\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"70636\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/c5a1d2/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> jbolger:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Perhaps the 14 day retention period is not applying to messages not yet delivered to the primary device?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>The retention period is actually 45 days. <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/avitus\">@Avitus</a> is mistaken.</p>",
